# Whitelist approach: ignore everything by default.
# This folder holds many unrelated project files (spreadsheets, docs,
# other dashboards, credentials) that must never end up in this
# PUBLIC repo. Only the dashboard's own files are tracked.
*

!.gitignore
!index.html
!balances.json
!fetch_balances.py
!vendor_breakdown.html
!.github/
!.github/**
